      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Bas Hamstra</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://www.quarkchess.de/csvn2001/body_index.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/BasHamstra.jpg/300px-BasHamstra.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"246\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/b/b1/BasHamstra.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:BasHamstra.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Bas Hamstra <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Bas Hamstra</b>,<br />\na Dutch software developer, and as computer chess programmer, author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and later <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Tao\" title=\"Tao\">Tao</a>. He was also involved in the early development of <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bookbuilder&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bookbuilder (page does not exist)\">Bookbuilder</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1997_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1997 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bas_Hamstra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery21.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Hamstra32.jpg\" src=\"/images/4/40/Hamstra32.jpg\" width=\"566\" height=\"417\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Elke_Van_Vlierberghe\" title=\"Elke Van Vlierberghe\">Elke Van Vlierberghe</a> and Bas Hamstra, <a href=\"/DOCCC_2004\" title=\"DOCCC 2004\">DOCCC 2004</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bas_Hamstra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1997_...\">1997 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bas_Hamstra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1997 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=11617\">Question to Amir Ban</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 05, 1997 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>&#160;» <a href=\"/Amir_Ban\" title=\"Amir Ban\">Amir Ban</a>, <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=13783\">Singular extensions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=65947\">What is the advantage of fail-soft?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 25, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=72400\">Tao</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bas_Hamstra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=109588\">Fast BB move generation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 08, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a>, <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=148342\">Temporal Difference</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Temporal_Difference_Learning\" title=\"Temporal Difference Learning\">Temporal Difference Learning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=149645\">Tao update</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=208714\">Aspiration window</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 20, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=210007\">CCT4 Tao/Quark</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 26, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT4\" title=\"CCT4\">CCT4</a>, <a href=\"/Quark\" title=\"Quark\">Quark</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=242621\">About Tao 5.2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=272739\">WHAT is the definition of a backward pawn?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Backward_Pawn\" title=\"Backward Pawn\">Backward Pawn</a>, <a href=\"/Backward_Pawns_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Backward Pawns (Bitboards)\">Backward Pawns (Bitboards)</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bas_Hamstra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29944\">LMR</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 30, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bas_Hamstra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=136\">Bas Hamstra's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bas_Hamstra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Bas Hamstra, <a href=\"/Martin_Giepmans\" title=\"Martin Giepmans\">Martin Giepmans</a> and arbiter <a href=\"/index.php?title=Rienk_Doetjes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Rienk Doetjes (page does not exist)\">Rienk Doetjes</a>, Photos from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.quarkchess.de/csvn2001/body_index.html\">1st CSVN-Tournament 2001</a> by <a href=\"/Thomas_Mayer\" title=\"Thomas Mayer\">Thomas Mayer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=242621\">About Tao 5.2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2002</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery21.html\">24th Open Dutch Computer-Chess Championship 2004 Photo Gallery</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/5fba0f94be869f35\">Search Degredation w/ C++</a> by Chris Jason Richards, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, June 12, 1997, post 4 and 6 by <a href=\"/Amir_Ban\" title=\"Amir Ban\">Amir Ban</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228163833\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 87/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 178/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key osca